mutation ($payload:BplusItSappiCreateChannelInput!)
{
	bplusItSappiCreateChannel (payload:$payload)
	{
		id
		tenantId
		systemId
		party
		component
		name
		flowParty
		flowComponent
		flowInterfaceName
		flowInterfaceNamespace
		adapterType
		direction
		transportProtocol
		messageProtocol
		adapterEngineName
		url
		username
		remoteHost
		remotePort
		directory
		fileSchema
		proxyHost
		proxyPort
		destination
		adapterStatus
		softwareComponentName
		responsibleUserAccountName
		lastChangeUserAccount
		lastChangedAt
		createdAt
		updatedAt
	}
}
